  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK259">
<l>avicorin tāyiram vēṭṭali ṉoṉṟi</l>
<l>ṉuyircekut tuṇṇāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not to kill and eat (the flesh of) an animal, is better than the pouring forth of ghee etc., in a thousand sacrifices.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
